{"id": "1422858158535086254", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1129096201887821844", "author_name": "ugen_22zi", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝！", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T08:10:20.421000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422908961501351966", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1236712268432015462", "author_name": "sakura_rts", "author_bot": false, "content": "どういう編成にしたらいいんだろう…\nニムフィーアさんは入れたいんだけども、初心者なので合うキャラがわからず…他キャラも育てれるくらいの素材はあります", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:32:12.792000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1422908960666550405", "filename": "IMG_1732.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1182943, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1422908960666550405/IMG_1732.png?ex=6a347ffc&is=6a332e7c&hm=0d3aec3890da1d808e2175807017969dc715d1dd3b61067b1f4c9540977c35be&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422912127492030495", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "993426658881196032", "author_name": "bgm0001", "author_bot": false, "content": "その手持ち内でってことですか？\n未所持をガチャで狙う気がありましたら、混沌以外を引くことを遅いけどオススメしたいです。\n狂魔(赤い牙の陣営)を使うなら、ファイントかアグリッパはほしいところ…\n深海(青い蛸足)使うなら、複数人当てる必要がありそう。\n超次元は、配布のエリカで最悪賄えるのでマイペースに楽しむくらいなら無理して引かなくてもいいです。\n\n強くて確実に楽できそうなのは限定キャラを引くこと\nでも無課金ならそんなに余裕はないだろうから石と相談かなぁ", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:44:47.623000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422908961501351966", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422912354462601226", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "ニムフィーア、ラモンナ、ナウティラ、カレン\nニムフィーア軸の混沌パで1番ランキング高く見る編成", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:45:41.737000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1236712268432015462"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422908961501351966", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422912495810773033", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "他の属性を混ぜる場合は狂魔を混ぜるのが毒を活かしやすいと思いますよー", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:46:15.437000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913078793736192", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "次のピック覚醒体のリリーがたぶん相性いいと思います\n楽しみに待ちましょう(混沌かつ毒)", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:48:34.431000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:48:48.799000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913129766981703", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1236712268432015462", "author_name": "sakura_rts", "author_bot": false, "content": "お二方ともありがとうございます！", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:48:46.584000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913198050508810", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "993426658881196032", "author_name": "bgm0001", "author_bot": false, "content": "たしかに次リリーだから相性よさそう", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:49:02.864000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913254514098237", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1236712268432015462", "author_name": "sakura_rts", "author_bot": false, "content": "なるほど…混沌染め、良さそう…石貯めておきます！", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:49:16.326000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["438289046993633281"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422913078793736192", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913345727762432", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "染めを意識してもいいし、狂魔をちょい足ししてもいいよ", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:49:38.073000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1236712268432015462"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422913254514098237", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913537067712605", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1236712268432015462", "author_name": "sakura_rts", "author_bot": false, "content": "なんか染めだと強くなるみたいなのあった気がするからそのボーナス活かして組もうかなぁと", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:50:23.692000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913546953429013", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "他の属性だと、テーマがブレちゃうかも", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:50:26.049000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913627924467843", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "界域知識がボーナスで+250されるよ", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:50:45.354000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1236712268432015462"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422913537067712605", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913805737922654", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "あと、混沌属性の界域の特性がキーオーダーを使った時にパーティの知識から計算した値の狂気がたまります", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:51:27.748000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422913896011796571", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "狂気も貯まりやすくなるんだなーって思えば良い", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:51:49.271000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422914162614468640", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "混ぜて複数属性になった場合は、ボーナスが消えて狂気の計算が半分になる\nメリットとデメリットがあるけど、他の属性の特性も活かせるからね", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:52:52.834000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422914353711157319", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1236712268432015462", "author_name": "sakura_rts", "author_bot": false, "content": "狂魔の回復的なのに結構救われたから余裕があれば狂魔も引こうかなぁ、無理はせずに", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:53:38.395000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422914419121324195", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1236712268432015462", "author_name": "sakura_rts", "author_bot": false, "content": "まずはリリーが最優先だけど", "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:53:53.990000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
